aboutWe curate the best infrastructure for you

GX

WIFI

GX Group is a European market leading Fiber-to-the-Home (FTTH) company with 20 years experience, focused on Manufacturing and Development of FTTH products. Quality and innovation is in our focus where we invest major part in our R&D team developing next generation PON (GPON/XGPON/XGSPON) solutions. Our motto is to build advanced Fiber products which can sustain the oncoming future demands for a Digital world

Our people are many things. Some are entrepreneurs, creators, developers and innovators. Others are thinkers, listeners, planners and strategists. They come from different cultures and diverse backgrounds. What connects them all is their passion and drive to develop in-home connectivity solutions that surpass our clients’ expectations. They are what make the company a success.
